profile.bio:
JestersArmy, DV survivor, cupcake baker, unrepentant infidel

I love to read books, pet my dog, and #StayFrosting

Dont ever tell me what to think I'll figure it out myself
Listen, then ask...
#PeopleAreAwesome #PeaceLoveFreedom #PayItForward
